* Rage snarled and shook her head as Cyber Claw struck at her with her optic 
lasers, she wasn't used to green things that hurt coming out of her prey.
Maybe she'd bit down to hard?
She was now almost famished and wasn't going to let such a small amount of 
pain detour her so easily and it tickled when the other raptor hopped up on 
her nose and peeked over the edge of it.
This WAS strange!
Prey automatically coming close to her mouth when so many had tried to stay 
away from it, what was this world coming to?
This raptor almost seemed to be saying, "Eat Me!"
That is...until it turned and attacked her eye!
Rage opened her mouth wide and bellowed as she felt the sharp claws of a 
raptor dig into her eye, she no longer cared about the strange thing that 
had changed in her mouth she just wanted to rip the one on her nose to 
bits!!!!
Rage shook her head from side to side and snapped out into thin air, her 
dinner plans had been ruined!!*
